  "verificationNotes": "Fetched and read the full arXiv 2408.11857 PDF (Hermes 3 Technical Report, arXiv watermark dated 15 Aug 2024, exactly matching record's release date). Table 5 'Final downstream task evaluations' literally shows all seven claimed Hermes-3-405B scores verbatim: MMLU 85.02 (5-shot), MMLU-PRO 54.14 (5-shot), GPQA 44.84 (0-shot), ARC-C 69.45 (0-shot), BBH 75.37 (3-shot), HellaSwag 90.19 (10-shot), TruthfulQA MC2 65.57 (0-shot). Paper confirms Llama 3.1 base sizes (8B/70B/405B) and 131,072 (128K) native context window. HF model card lists 406B raw param count vs. the record's standard '405B' naming; kept 405 as this is the universally used name for this Llama 3.1 size class. No changes made."
